¶ The ship set ground
     on the shore ¶

00:40.841 --> 00:43.708
¶ Of this uncharted
      desert isle ¶

00:43.777 --> 00:45.910
¶ With Gilligan ¶

00:45.979 --> 00:48.112
¶ The Skipper too ¶

00:48.181 --> 00:50.315
¶ The millionaire ¶

00:50.384 --> 00:52.751
¶ And his wife ¶

00:52.820 --> 00:55.587
¶ The movie star ¶

00:55.656 --> 00:57.556
¶ And the rest ¶

